    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient accuracy for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. The relative hemolysis index RH is below 1.0 for the predicate comparison at all five operating points. The six unassessed factors are appropriately scoped out per MRL 2 requirements. The model is accepted for use in the CPB COU.",
